339
00:21:41,440 --> 00:21:43,189
She would never say that.

340
00:21:43,480 --> 00:21:45,758
She and Shen Mochen
had an arranged marriage from childhood.

341
00:21:45,759 --> 00:21:47,109
Didn't you know?

342
00:21:47,200 --> 00:21:48,318
Stop looking for her.

343
00:21:48,319 --> 00:21:50,030
Even if you do, you won't find her.

344
00:21:50,680 --> 00:21:52,230
I'll find her no matter what.

345
00:21:54,119 --> 00:21:55,070
Siyan!

